data.title: FIFA soundtrack: All songs in FIFA 23 and the previous games
data.meta_description: Every FIFA soundtrack ever, from FIFA 23 to FIFA Road to World Cup 98.
data.text:
Whatever mood you're in, the FIFA soundtracks have always provided hit after hit. With classics like Avicii's The Nights in FIFA 15 and Blur's Song 2 in Road to World Cup 98, there's always an iconic FIFA song to enjoy.

Advertisement

FIFA 23 is no different and brings the hits with over 100 songs across all its different modes. As usual, you'll find hits from well-known stars including Gorillaz to the lesser-known up-and-coming artists on its soundtrack.

No matter what FIFA game's soundtrack you want to listen to, we've got you covered.

Join us below for a kick-about down memory lane, with a look back at EVERY soundtrack from FIFA 23 all the way back to World Cup 98 when Beckham was on the cover.
